data.description: Exceptional two story situated on an extensively landscaped interior lot in Lakewood Forest. Recent roof with radiant barrier decking, masonry siding, granite counter tops in the kitchen and bathrooms, and recent exterior paint are just a few of this home's many updates. Features such as larger covered patio, huge back yard, two fireplaces, and block paneling make this one of the most sought after properties in Lakewood Forest. Call today and make this incredible house your new home.
